Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God in Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will blood be shed in this forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:18.96,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(342,0)\pos(354,346)}Child's Play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:42.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,121)\pos(358,57)}Another child falls to his death... \N Is it an accident, or suicide!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:48.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(400,75)\pos(357,40)}Dangerous children's game? \N Yet another victim!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:54.99,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(400,75)\pos(356,41)}And now, a fifth victim... \N Further restrictions on rooftop access implemented!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,79)\pos(356,385)}Ralf Ludwig Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing on the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.61,0:03:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me anything you can remember,\Nno matter how small it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to him, Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't hit the first floor awning and\Ngotten caught on the tree branch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could've died
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, talk to the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make sure you won't do\Nanything foolish like that again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if he had died, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to provide your son with counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk outside, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter, just sit right there and wait for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go into the room or anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he... your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. I'm Just taking care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... Dieter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does what hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, where you got hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under your bandages...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was scary, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you fell off the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shoes are in that bag right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to lie down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna get mad at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if they get mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm afraid of them getting\Nmad at me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once you come back to life, go outside."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The world will have changed..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the world that's changed, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bored...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know the world was so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! He's scared
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't want to die!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Help me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me if I was scared when\NI fell off the roof, didn't you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I wasn't scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was all a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But a lot of children died
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stand on the edges of abandoned\Nbuildings' roofs, facing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we close our eyes and move\Ntowards each other, step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not you fail, as long\Nas you live, you're the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make a bet with fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who lives is chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who lives can play the game again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this world is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those chosen by fate can keep playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 thought you were one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a true idiot if you don't \N understand after seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going up to the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chosen ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the superior ones will survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's {\i1}the{\i0} one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who taught us this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's our friend, a friend of the superior children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to understand. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still siding with them even\Nafter they did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to be buried\Nin this stupid world after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come and see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of the view?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, close your eyes and try to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.39,0:11:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really understand what you're trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the world was pitch black...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the future was filled with darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a really good sausage the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I die, I'll never be able to have it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love playing soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.84,0:11:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I die, I'll never be able to kick the ball again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:11:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1 like Dr. Reichwein!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His secretary, Ms. Mehres, is nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I die, I won't be able to see them again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary things will never go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he said we have to become adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma said that tomorrow will be a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, I won't get to see Tenma anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:12:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bend down, slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be like Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan's playing a much better game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan said that he'll be killed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he'll be shot and \N killed by some Japanese guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really walked on the edge of\Nthe roof with my eyes closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't scared at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I opened my eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joachim, who should have been walking towards\Nme from the other side, had disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the moment a person \N dies with my very own eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People really do die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that son of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to understand what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that he's alive but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I think about how Joachim's parents\Nmust feel after losing their son...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to listen to what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She nags at me like that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't let me out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't even let me watch TV or read comic books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.26,0:14:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're not allowed to read comic books...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,picture books are okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, picture books?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is that great game you mentioned\Nthe other day going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you might get shot soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is that Japanese guy going to shoot you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Johan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermann Hesse...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first printing of Steppenwolf
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another first printing of Hoffman's Nachtestücke
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a complete set of Goethe's poems
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear God...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I, the director of the University of Munich's\NFriedrich Emmanuel Library...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am dazzled by your collection of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I taught myself everything I know, because\NI wasn't able to go to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought I'd at least read books, and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you'd donate such a\Ncollection of books to our library
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even find the words to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going blind, and can't read them anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than have them sleep in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they would be more useful in the hands of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they're very valuable...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're also meant to be read by the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've also decided on where to store them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the ceremony to plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so please come to the library and we'll discuss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the security?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Mr. Schuwald started to appear in public...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've been concerned about the activities\Nof certain dangerous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be thorough when you check the invited guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan and Karl should go to the\Nlibrary and check things out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they're the ones who came up with\Nthe idea of donating this collection of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the director, Germann.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:17:01.42,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,387)}University of Münich Library
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will become the room that will house\NMr. Schuwald's collection of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary reader won't have access to this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have never been in here, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An optimal preservation temperature\Nand humidity are used.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is also protected against theft and fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of books here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a treasure for humanity, don't you think, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity's treasure, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And right over here in the central hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is where we're planning to hold the\Nbook collection donation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like his butler said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll put our full effort into the security.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want Mr. Schuwald to relax and \N attend the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Father will be happy to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if there are any good\Npicture books for my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Don't you think the art is wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think this is more suitable for adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your friend isn't an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm pretty clumsy, so this happens to me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the pictures are nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who wrote it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emil... Sebe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The publisher is Moravian...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it s a publisher in Prague, in the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of good picture book\Nauthors in the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never heard of Sebe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's not that famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.43,0:21:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, the heat this summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbearable...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:41.26,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(356,44)}Announcement regarding the donation of\NHans Georg Schuwald's book collection \N as well as Mr. Schuwald s speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:31.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(175,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:44.68,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:44.68,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,23)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:47.64,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:23:01.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:23:01.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(191,20)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.92,0:23:26.18,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,474)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:34.60,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(189,471)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,471)}Make it home
